original: Åkerblad, Sven Julius, kyrkoherde, Backaryd, f. 23/12/97 i Övraby, Hall. 1., av folkskoll. Sven Å. o. Sofia Jönsson. G. 29 m. Alma Elida Persson. Barn: Birgitta f. 30, Lena 34, Malin 37, Sven 43. — Stud:ex. i Lund 18, teol. fil. ex. där 24, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Lunds stift 26. Kyrko-adj. i Dalköpinge 29, kyrkoh. i Backaryd sed. 32. Ordf. i kyrkostämma o. skolstyr.
translated: Åkerblad, Sven Julius, vicar, Backaryd, born on December 23, 1897 in Övraby, Halland. Son of Sven Å. and Sofia Jönsson. Married on the 29th with Alma Elida Persson. Children: Birgitta born in 1930, Lena in 1934, Malin in 1937, Sven in 1943. — Bachelor of Arts in Lund in 1918, Bachelor of Theology there in 1924, Master of Theology, completed practical theology examination, and ordained as a priest in the Diocese of Lund in 1926. Church assistant in Dalköpinge in 1929, parish vicar in Backaryd since 1932. Chairman of the church assembly and school board.
